  ],
  "remarks": "Olga Koludarova is the Minister of Education and Science of the so-called “Donetsk People’s Republic”. She is one of the persons involved in the deportation of children from Ukraine to re-educate them in the Russian Federation. In her re-education programmes, she cooperates with Ramsan Kadyrov and the “Movement of the First”, a state-led youth organisation in the Russian Federation, which was created in December 2022 at the initiative of President of the Russian Federation Vladimir Putin to provide educational activities, including of a militarised nature, for children between the ages of 6 to 18, based on “traditional Russian spiritual and moral goals”.",
